project benefit, cost, timeline. accurate predictions make easy decisions. the agent can pursue projects with the rank order highest predicted return on investment ratio. these predictions can change in real time, making the prioritization of projects responsive to changing conditions. some projects have time limitations, such as preparing to sell sweaters before the winter, so the timeline prediction is necessary to decide timing.

